IPA thats been bombarded with Citra, Citra Incognito, Citra Lupomax, Riwaka and Strata
hops. Expect an orchard’s worth of citrus and
tropical fruity flavours.

items.badge_description: Lovers of little green cones rejoice. National IPA Day is pretty much like your best birthday! Whether you love hazies, milkshake, double, triple, or even quad IPAs just check in one today to earn this coveted badge.

A global celebration of beer, International Beer Day toasts to beers from all across the globe. Like a helles from Germany, a tripel from Belgian, or an ESB from Britain. Cheers to you, wherever you might be in the world!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 235 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 48! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

items.checkin_comment: Light and hazy, a bit citrusy and a little piney. Fresh and fruity, very drinkable.

user.bio: I fear my last words will be ‘‘hold my beer and watch this.’’

Keeping my friends close,
 but my beers closer.
Beer, whiskey and coffee are my loves! I use the uni scoring system for my ratings, and love both strong and light beers
